				<title>Dark-Mode Light-Mode Css</title>
				<description> Use a media query to set different values for variables in dark-mode.
:root { --background-color: #eee; --text-color: #222; } @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) { :root { --background-color: #222; --text-color: #eee; } } body { background-color: var(--background-color); color: var(--text-color); } </description>
